{"tid":1018124,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"嫲嫲入左醫院 集氣之餘 想上黎放下負能量","createTime":"2019-02-12T04:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T02:19:45.000Z","uid":4681,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8815d38ca1d0de33663b45668fe887b0d01d4eff","tid":1018124,"uid":4681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:14:12.000Z","msg":"講下背景先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我嫲嫲80有8 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有老人痴呆症<br />\n我唔知算有幾嚴重 不過佢係會每3分鐘問自己係邊到<br />\n同問我係邊個 見到幻覺 又話見到有個男人<br />\n(夜媽媽話見到個細路 我都真係好撚驚)<br />\n<br />\n係新年間 我嫲嫲夜晚自己去廁所<br />\n唔小心跌倒 要入骨科 <br />\n今日已經第4日 暫時都未出到時<br />\n小便都去唔到 著尿片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日仲要插尿喉<br />\n我同屋企人已經24小時睇住我嫲<br />\n但因為成日落床 護士都唔想煩  決定插<br />\n<br />\n眼見好多病人 有啲仲要訓路邊<br />\n嫲 屬於麻煩多口 成日想落床<br />\n因為傷及頸所有都唔可以落床<br />\n如果無我地睇住 就好麻煩<br />\n仲有老人痴呆影響 記憶交錯<br />\n連自己跌倒 送左去醫院都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我只係幫我嫲一個換尿片 俾佢ee哦哦下<br />\n條腰已經開始痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n試諗下 護士要幫幾多人處理呢啲事<br />\n明白有啲護士有幾攰<br />\n都知到有啲護士會好西 係因為太攰 太多野做<br />\n但我相信 唔係個個都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要照顧老人家真係好辛苦<br />\n有時候 仲要俾老人家鬧下<br />\n但我隔住個窗簾 聽到我嫲話 好痛 好辛苦<br />\n我個心真係 好痛 好痛<br />\n乜都幫唔到佢 可以做既只可能照顧下佢<br />\n啲回憶出返哂黎<br />\n好驚<br />\n<br />\n我唔係黑心 健康既長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好似我嫲嫲 又糖尿病 又白內障 又心臟疾病<br />\n依家行動有問題 我睇見都覺得辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a23282980d5c58987a14e9ed171425a2753037","tid":1018124,"uid":210161,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:16:44.000Z","msg":"我唔明集氣有咩撚野用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過<br />\n都希望你嫲嫲早日康復 身體健康"},{"pid":"c57102e509c93cf5f4263a4c909cb67909935291","tid":1018124,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:17:07.000Z","msg":"我老豆都就70<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望兩老可以健健康康咁過多十幾年，唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32cac4c85fff10bebd8e158fdaead715ad2fc937","tid":1018124,"uid":185670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:17:26.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431ea2e6626a7a4d5ac266a1ff46309952595679","tid":1018124,"uid":4681,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"97a23282980d5c58987a14e9ed171425a2753037","tid":1018124,"uid":210161,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:16:44.000Z","msg":"我唔明集氣有咩撚野用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過<br />\n都希望你嫲嫲早日康復 身體健康"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:17:29.000Z","msg":"集氣無用咖<br />\n係一種自我安慰<br />\n<br />\n多謝你"},{"pid":"4dbebf710ca2aa4854ec0686a2ffec97ccc9eb85","tid":1018124,"uid":196550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:19:29.000Z","msg":"我屋企人都七十幾 希望大家都健健康康"},{"pid":"8d2d16c879cc48be709338b9321117c5adb32802","tid":1018124,"uid":4681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c57102e509c93cf5f4263a4c909cb67909935291","tid":1018124,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:17:07.000Z","msg":"我老豆都就70<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望兩老可以健健康康咁過多十幾年，唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:20:33.000Z","msg":"得閒陪下2老"},{"pid":"0865ccd807f3b7c2c1c92a8da2657c54151e80b9","tid":1018124,"uid":5793,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:41:12.000Z","msg":"集氣for what先<br />\n集氣想佢快啲離開人間定快啲好翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e50d11d95380f0568a29119bc126e4633a8ada3","tid":1018124,"uid":10453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:51:11.000Z","msg":"好生不如好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a1b1e710c3f7b912b34ee99e6b25c68a3961b5","tid":1018124,"uid":207482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T01:21:11.000Z","msg":"香港公營醫療系統真係好有問題 點解啲環境差到咁 斷左鎖骨？ 見物理治療見成點？"},{"pid":"1c93c8990e1acc734b567f37f38b9c05b96af7e7","tid":1018124,"uid":4681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c4a1b1e710c3f7b912b34ee99e6b25c68a3961b5","tid":1018124,"uid":207482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T01:21:11.000Z","msg":"香港公營醫療系統真係好有問題 點解啲環境差到咁 斷左鎖骨？ 見物理治療見成點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:42:07.000Z","msg":"其實今次入到去先睇知係幾有問題<br />\n就算係有啲護士幾有心<br />\n個機制搞到頹<br />\n<br />\n本身我嫲入院第二日 要睇精神科<br />\n咁就提早左6個鐘 同當值護士講<br />\n點知個護士話 無收到通知 亦都話我同佢地講得太遲<br />\n要再約<br />\n<br />\n打過去精神科再問又話同當值醫生講<br />\n<br />\n等當值醫生到 又講幫我地send個email去精神科<br />\n叫佢地上黎<br />\n亦都補底 話唔知佢地幾時得間上 講唔定時間<br />\n<br />\n過2個鐘又話 做左腦素描 我嫲個腦有個血泡<br />\n要等腦外科黎睇 但又講唔定時間<br />\n骨就無事啦 所以佢地骨科做唔到啲咩<br />\n變相唔知等到幾時<br />\n等到有啲灰。。。"},{"pid":"f577a3793bb7c1ae683cb1654eeb1536fd98d2b9","tid":1018124,"uid":132896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:38:17.000Z","msg":"佢鐘意食啲咩呀<br />\n<br />\n諗定出院食啲咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我麻都差唔多咁既年紀<br />\n有時買啲零食比佢 佢會好開心"},{"pid":"c0039021a247ce4265bbf59d743b6fa5b6779e6f","tid":1018124,"uid":4681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f577a3793bb7c1ae683cb1654eeb1536fd98d2b9","tid":1018124,"uid":132896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:38:17.000Z","msg":"佢鐘意食啲咩呀<br />\n<br />\n諗定出院食啲咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我麻都差唔多咁既年紀<br />\n有時買啲零食比佢 佢會好開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T06:49:41.000Z","msg":"糖尿病無得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係之前食太好"},{"pid":"785fd04ac7f4922825d84105368a62cedf8e287c","tid":1018124,"uid":37162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T00:04:30.000Z","msg":"咁有嫲嫲心 你真係乖 <br />\n<br />\n嫲嫲會冇事架<br />\n<br />\n不過都係果句 發生乜事都好<br />\n拎上黎連登問 有時候都係哂氣 令自己更負能量<br />\n不過見你好似上面咁樣覆番人 你真係大個左唔小"},{"pid":"c31d70d9ae93ca3fe6c23be7338144e8ae4b81ce","tid":1018124,"uid":22409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T00:25:08.000Z","msg":"安樂死應該合法化<br />\n對呢個社會百利而無一害"},{"pid":"ca99b51ac2ce4f9ceb1f2d082cc49ca104d506b0","tid":1018124,"uid":36050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T00:31:23.000Z","msg":"婆婆有冇排開院舍？會唔會有醫務社工跟 如果照顧上有問題可以留個tg傾下 利申做緊長者鄰舍中心社工 跟開認知障礙症case"},{"pid":"103a5a9d56b798807e929e575dc82a74574d1c87","tid":1018124,"uid":114671,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T00:47:06.000Z","msg":"有啲人鍾意笑人口德邨，到佢屋企自己有老嘢或家人病危時就知點解"},{"pid":"dce06658fc8e7690d9fb0b8c5e745c928bbad0ef","tid":1018124,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T00:53:14.000Z","msg":"插尿喉會易左入菌先多併發症  仲煩 仲多野搞<br />\n點會係因為懶/忙"},{"pid":"c20491d8137a950dc77f6b2414a245b3f5e60839","tid":1018124,"uid":4681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dce06658fc8e7690d9fb0b8c5e745c928bbad0ef","tid":1018124,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T00:53:14.000Z","msg":"插尿喉會易左入菌先多併發症  仲煩 仲多野搞<br />\n點會係因為懶/忙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:19:45.000Z","msg":"所以換片換到幾攰 我都幫佢換<br />\n不過護士見到佢小便有困難 已經儲到700cc<br />\n一定要放尿"}]}